### Branch Naming

```
feat/component-name
fix/issue-description
refactor/what-changed
docs/topic
chore/task
```

Examples:
- `feat/button`
- `feat/icon-container`
- `fix/input-focus-state`
- `refactor/card-composition`
- `docs/component-guide`

### Commit Messages

Use conventional commits:

```
type(scope): description

[optional body]

[optional footer]
```

Types:
- `feat`: New feature
- `fix`: Bug fix
- `refactor`: Code refactoring
- `docs`: Documentation
- `style`: Code style (formatting)
- `test`: Tests
- `chore`: Build/tooling

Examples:
```
feat(button): add primary and secondary variants

- Implement Base UI Button wrapper
- Add cva variant management
- Create Storybook stories

Closes #123
```

